1. Executive Overview
The One Step Challenge is Doji Funding's flagship evaluation product targeting flexible traders seeking an optimal balance between risk and reward. It features a single evaluation phase with fully customizable parameters, adaptive rules, and transparent risk-based pricing.
1.1 Target Audience
Intermediate to advanced traders who want speed and flexibility. The single-phase evaluation reduces time-to-funding to 5-10 days while maintaining robust risk controls.
1.2 Key Differentiators
Single Phase Evaluation: One target to hit, one set of rules to follow. No Phase 2 complexity.
Full Parameter Customization: Profit target, loss limits, split, days, consistency - all adjustable with real-time price recalculation.
Adaptive Rule Engine: News trading, weekend holding, and copy trading permissions adapt automatically based on the chosen configuration.
Risk-Based Pricing: Easier configurations cost more; harder ones cost less. The price always reflects the firm's actual risk exposure.
Promo Code Support: Percentage or fixed-amount discount codes with a floor at 30% of base price to prevent abuse.
